\c 18
\s Hezekia mambo waJudha
\p
\v 1 Zvino negore rechitatu raHoshea mwanakomana waEra mambo waIsraeri, Hezekia mwanakomana waAhazi mambo waJudha wakatanga kubata ushe.
\v 2 Akatanga kubata ushe ava wemakore makumi maviri namashanu; akabata ushe paJerusarema makore makumi maviri namapfumbamwe; zita ramai vake rakange riri Abhi mukunda waZekariya.
\v 3 Akaita zvakarurama pamberi paJehovha, sezvakaita baba vake Dhavhidhi.
\p
\v 4 Akabvisa matunhu akakwirira, akaputsa shongwe, akaparadza matanda okunamata nawo; akaputsaputsa nyoka yendarira yakange yakaitwa naMozisi; nokuti kusvikira pamazuva iwayo vana vaIsraeri vaiipisira zvinonhuhwira; akaitumidza Nehushitani.
\v 5 Akatenda kuna Jehovha Mwari waIsraeri; naizvozvo hakuna wakange akafanana naye pakati pamadzimambo ese aJudha, kuna vakamutevera kana akamutangira.
\v 6 Nokuti wakanamatira Jehovha, haana kutsauka pakumutevera; asi wakachengeta mirairo yake, yakarairwa Mozisi naJehovha.
\v 7 Jehovha akava naye; kwese kwaakaenda wakafambiswa zvakanaka; akamukira mambo weAsiriya, akasamushumira.
\v 8 Akakunda VaFirisitia kusvikira paGaza nemiganhu yaro, kubva pachirindo chomurindi kusvikira pamaguta akakombwa norusvingo.
\p
\v 9 Zvino negore rechina ramambo Hezekia, riri gore rechinomwe raHoshea mwanakomana waEra mambo waIsraeri, Sharimaneseri mambo weAsiriya akanorwa neSamaria, akarikomba.
\v 10 Pakupera kwamakore matatu vakarikunda; Samaria rikakundwa negore retanhatu raHezekia, riri gore repfumbamwe raHoshea mambo waIsraeri.
\v 11 Mambo weAsiriya akatapa VaIsraeri, akaenda navo Asiriya, akavaisa paHara, napaHabhori, parwizi Gozani, nomumaguta avaMedhih.
\v 12 Nokuti havana kuteerera inzwi raJehovha Mwari wavo, asi vakadarika sungano yake, izvo zvese zvavakange varairwa naMozisi muranda waJehovha, vakaramba kunzwa, kana kuzviita.
\s Saniheribhi mambo weAsiriya anokomba Jerusarema, asi vaJudha vanorwirwa naJehovha
\p
\v 13 Zvino negore regumi namana ramambo Hezekia, Saniheribhi mambo weAsiriya akanorwa namaguta ese aJudha akakombwa namasvingo, akaakunda.
\v 14 Zvino Hezekia mambo weJudha akatuma shoko kuna mambo weAsiriya paRakishi, akati: Ndatadza, dzokai henyu mubve kwandiri; zvese zvamunoreva kwandiri ndichazviripa. Ipapo mambo weAsiriya akaripisa Hezekia mambo weJudha matarenda ana mazana matatu esirivha namatarenda ana makumi matatu egoridhe.
\v 15 Hezekia akamupa sirivha yese yakange iri mumba maJehovha, napafuma yeimba yamambo.
\v 16 Nenguva iyo Hezekia wakabvisa goridhe pamikova yeimba yaJehovha, napambiru dzakange dzafukidzwa nayo naHezekia mambo waJudha, akaipa mambo weAsiriya.
\v 17 Zvino mambo weAsiriya akatuma mukuru wehondo, nomukuru wamachinda, nomukuru wavatariri vabve Rakishi nehondo huru vaende kuna Hezekia paJerusarema. Ivo vakaenda, vakasvika Jerusarema. Zvino vakati vasvika, vakamira pamugero wedziva rokumusoro, riri panzira huru inoenda kumunda womusuki.
\v 18 Zvino vakati vadana mambo, Eriakimu mwanakomana waHirikia, waichengeta imba, naShebhana munyori, naJoa mwanakomana waAsafi sahwira, va kabudira kwavari.
\v 19 Zvino mukuru wavatariri akati kwavari: Zvino imwi muti kuna Hezekia: Zvanzi namambo mukuru, mambo weAsiriya: Chaunovimba nacho chinyi?
\v 20 Iwe unoti (asi mashoko omuromo hawo), mano nesimba zvokurwa nazvo zviripo hazvo. Zvino unovimba naniko, zvawandimukira ini?
\v 21 Tarira zvino, unovimba nomudonzvo worutsanga urwu rwakapwanyika, Egipita, runoti kana munhu akasendama kwaruri, ruchapinda muruoko rwake, rukamubaya; ndizvo zvakaita Farao mambo weEgipita kuna vese vanovimba naye.
\v 22 Asi kana ukati kwandiri: Tinovimba naJehovha Mwari wedu, ko haasi iye wakabvisirwa matunhu akakwirira nearitari dzake naHezekia, akati kuna Judha naJerusarema: Munofanira kunamata pamberi pearitari iri paJerusarema, here?
\v 23 Naizvozvo zvino, chipikiranai henyu natenzi wangu mambo weAsiriya, ndikupe mabhiza ane zvuru zviviri, kana iwe ukagona kuisa vatasvi pamusoro pawo.
\v 24 Ungagona sei kukunda mukuru umwe kuna vadiki vavaranda vatenzi vangu, kana ukavimba naEgipita kuti upiwe ngoro namabhiza navo?
\v 25 Ini ndauya kuzorwa nenzvimbo iyi kuti ndiiparadze ndisina Jehovha here? Ndiye Jehovha wakati kwandiri: Enda undorwa nenyika iyo, uiparadze.
\v 26 Ipapo Eriakimu mwanakomana waHirikia, naShebhana, naJoa vakati kumukuru wavatariri: Tinokumbira kuti mutaure henyu navaranda venyu norurimi rwechiAramaia, nokuti tinochinzwisisa; murege henyu kutaura nesu norurimi rwavaJudha, vanhu vese vari parusvingo vazvinzwe.
\v 27 Asi mukuru wavatariri wakati kwaari: Tenzi wangu wakandituma kuna tenzi wako nokwauri here, kuti nditaure mashoko awa? Haana kundituma here kuvanhu vagere pamusoro porusvingo, kuti vadye ndove yavo nemvura yavo pamwe chete nemi?
\v 28 Ipapo mukuru wavatariri akamira, akadanidzira nenzwi guru norurimi rwavaJudha, akataura achiti: Inzwai shoko ramambo mukuru, iye mambo weAsiriya.
\v 29 Zvanzi namambo: Hezekia ngaarege kukunyengerai; nokuti haagoni kukurwirai pamaoko ake;
\v 30 Hezekia ngaarege kukuvimbisai naJehovha, achiti Jehovha uchatirwira zvirokwazvo, uye kuti guta iri haringaiswi mumaoko amambo weAsiriya.
\v 31 Musateerera Hezekia, nokuti zvanzi namambo weAsiriya: Yananai neni, mubudirei kwandiri, mudye umwe neumwe muzambiringa wake, umwe neumwe muwonde wake, umwe neumwe mvura yetsime rake;
\v 32 kusvikira ini ndauya ndikutorei, ndikuisei kunyika yakafanana neyenyu, nyika ine zviyo newaini, nyika ine chingwa neminda yemizambiringa, nyika inamafuta emiorivhi nouchi, murarame, murege kufa, regai kuteerera Hezekia, kana achikugombedzerai achiti: Jehovha uchatirwira.
\v 33 Ko umwe wavamwari vendudzi wakatomborwira nyika yake paruoko rwamambo weAsiriya here?
\v 34 Vamwari veHamati neAripadhi varipi? Vamwari veSefarivhaimi, neHena, neIvha varipi vakarwira Samaria paruoko rwangu here?
\v 35 Ndavapiko pakati pavamwari vese venyika vakarwira nyika yavo paruoko rwangu, zvamunoti Jehovha ucharwira Jerusarema paruoko rwangu?
\v 36 Asi vanhu vakaramba vanyerere, havana kumupindura shoko rimwe, nokuti murairo wamambo wakange uchiti: Regai kumupindura.
\v 37 Zvino Eriakimu mwanakomana waHirikia, waitarira imba, naShebha munyori, naJoa, mwanakomana waAsafi sahwira, vakaenda kuna Hezekia, nguvo dzavo dzabvarurwa, vakamuudza mashoko omukuru wavatariri.